Integration tests using  flutter driver.
========================================

Before running this test, remove all data from the backend system:
terminal:   ./gradlew cleandb
            java -jar moqui.war load types=seed,seed-initial,install
            java -jar moqui.war

flutter driver On mobile. (can make screenshots)
-------------------------
start your mobile emulator:
list: flutter emulators
launch: flutter emulators --launch >>name<<

to start test: flutter drive \
    --driver=test_driver/menu_test.dart \
    --target=test_driver/target.dart


flutter driver on chrome:  (can make screenshots)
-------------------------
download chromedriver and install in path: https://flutter.dev/docs/cookbook/testing/integration/introduction#6b-web

start in a terminal:
./chromedriver --port=4444

another terminal : (only works on release mode)
    flutter drive \
    --driver=test_driver/menu_test.dart \
    --target=test_driver/target.dart \
    --browser-name=chrome \
    --no-headless --release


To make screenshots see: android/fastlane/README or ios/fastlane/README
-----------------------------------------------------------------------



